      "y": 3320,
      "width": 420,
      "height": 160,
      "text": "## [GitHub Pages 公開の骨格を作る](docs/exec-plans/chunks/chunk-2026-03-10-014-pages-publish-skeleton.md)\n`CHUNK-2026-03-10-014`\nstatus: `done`\ntickets: `2`",
